# Line endings policy (cross-platform / edge-first)
#
# Intent:
# - Keep repository blobs canonical as LF to avoid CRLF noise and shell/shebang issues in Linux/Docker.
# - Developers on Windows should rely on editor settings; Git will enforce the canonical form.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Common binary types (never normalize)
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.mp4 binary
*.onnx binary
*.pt binary
*.zip binary
*.tar binary
*.gz binary
*.pdf binary

